ilm)|The King of Kings]]'' (1927) \n* ''[[The Great Commandment]]'' (1939) \n* ''Day of Triumph'' (1954) \n* ''[[King of Kings (1961 film)|King of Kings]]'' (1961) \n* ''[[The Greatest Story Ever Told]]'' (1965) \n* ''Wednesday Play: Son of Man'' (1969) (UK)\n* ''[[Godspell (film)|Godspell]]'' (1973) \n* ''Gospel Road: A Story of Jesus'' (1973) \n* ''[[Jesus Christ Superstar (film)|Jesus Christ Superstar]]'' (1973) \n* ''[[The Passover Plot (film)|The Passover Plot]]'' (1976) \n* ''[[Jesus of Nazareth (miniseries)|Jesus of Nazareth]]'' (1977 miniseries) (Italy) (UK)\n* ''[[The Nativity (film)|The Nativity]]'' (1978, TV)\n* ''[[Jesus (1979 film)|Jesus]]'' (1979)\n* ''The New Media Bible: The Gospel According to St. Luke'' (1979) \n* ''A Child Called Jesus'' (1987)\n* ''[[The Last Temptation of Christ (film)|The Last Temptation of Christ]]'' (1988) \n* ''The Revolutionary'' (1995)\n* ''The Revolutionary II'' (1996)\n* ''[[The Visual Bible: Matthew]]'' (1997) (South Africa)\n* ''[[Jesus (1999 film)|Jesus]]'' (1999, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[The Gospel of John (film)|The Gospel of John]]'' (2003) (Canada/UK)\n* ''[[Son of Man (2006 film)|Son of Man]]'' (2006) (South Africa)\n* ''[[Color of the Cross]]'' (2006) \n* ''The First Christmas (Liken Bible Series)'' (2006) \n* ''[[The Nativity Story]]'' (2006) \n* ''[[The Passion (TV serial)|The Passion]]'' (2008 miniseries) (UK)\n* ''The Road to Emmaus'' (2009) \n* ''[[The Nativity (2010 TV series)|The Nativity]]'' (2010 miniseries) (UK)\n* ''[[Killing Jesus]]''  (2013) \n* ''[[Son of God (film)|Son of God]]'' (2014) \n* ''[[Last Days in the Desert]]'' (2015)\n* ''[[The Young Messiah]]'' (2016) \n* ''[[Risen (2016 film)|Risen]]'' (2016)\n* ''[[The Chosen (TV series)]]'' (2017\u2060\u2014Present)\n* ''[[Jesus: His Life]]'' (2019 History channel miniseries) \n}}\n\n==== Spanish ====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''Jes\u00fas de Nazareth'' (1942) (Mexico)\n* ''[[Mar\u00eda Magdalena: Pecadora de Magdala]]'' (1945) (Mexico)\n* 