roject.<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.revelationmedia.com | title = The Animated Bible Series | website = revelationmedia.com | language = en | access-date = Sep 24, 2018 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180822143540/https://www.revelationmedia.com/ | archive-date = August 22, 2018 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n}}\n\n=== Mary, Mother of Jesus ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n*'' [[Saint Mary (film)|Saint Mary]] (2000) (Iran)\n* ''[[Mary, Mother of Jesus (film)|Mary, Mother of Jesus]]'' (1999, TV) \n* ''[[Marie de Nazareth]] (1995) (France) \n* ''[[Mary of Nazareth (film)|Mary of Nazareth]] 2012 (Italy) \n* '' Full of Grace '' (2015) \n}}\n\n===Herod the Great===\n* ''[[Herod the Great (film)|Erode il Grande]]'' (1959) (Italy)\n\n===Mary Magdalene===\n* ''The Friends of Jesus - Mary Magdalene''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0244647/releaseinfo</ref> (2000)\n* ''[[Mary Magdalene (2018 film)|Mary Magdalene]]'' (2018)\n\n===Salome===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''Salome'' (1908) \n* ''[[Salom\u00e8 (1910 film)]]'' (Italy)\n* ''[[Salome (1918 film)|Salome]]'' (1918) \n* ''[[Salome (1923 film)|Salome]]'' (1923) \n* ''[[Salome (1953 film)|Salome]]'' (1953) \n* ''[[Salome (1972 film)]] (Italy)\n* ''Salome'' (1978) (Spain)\n* ''[[Salom\u00e8 (1986 film)]]'' (Italy-France)\n* ''[[Salome's Last Dance]]'' (1988) (UK)\n* ''[[Salom\u00e9 (2002 film)|Salome]]'' (2002) (Spain)\n* ''[[Salome]]'' (2007)\n* ''[[Wilde Salom\u00e9]]'' (2011) (documentary-drama film)\n* ''[[Salom\u00e9 (2013 film)]]''\n}}\n\n===Judas Iscariot===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Blade af Satans bog]]'' (1920) (Denmark)\n* ''El beso de Judas'' (1953) (Spain)\n* ''[[Neither Are We Enemies]]'' (1970-TV) \n* ''The Friends of Jesus - Judas''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0253101/releaseinfo</ref> (2001)\n* ''[[Judas (2004 film)|Judas]]'' (2004) \n* ''[[Story of Judas]]'' (2015) (France)\n}}\n\n===Barabbas===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Barabbas (1953 film)|Barabbas]]'' (1953) (Sweden)\n* ''Give Us Barabbas''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0215807/</ref> (1961-TV) \n* ''[[Barabbas (1961 film)|Barabbas]]'' (1961)\n* ''Barabbas'' (1964) (Belgium)\n* ''[[Barabbas (2012 film)|Barabbas]]'' (2012 - TV) \n}}\n\n===Parable of the Prodigal Son===\n* ''[[L'Enfant prodigue (film)|L'Enfant prodigue]]'' (1907) (France)\n* ''L'Enfant prodigue'' (1916) (France)\n* ''[[The Prodigal]]'' (1955)\n\n===Life of the Apostles===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[The Big Fisherman]]'' (1959)\n* ''[[Peter and Paul (film)|Peter and Paul]]'' (1981-TV)\n* ''[[A.D. (miniseries)|A.D.]]'' (1985 miniseries)\n* ''[[The Visual Bible: Acts]]'' (1994) \n* ''The Emissary''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0219668/</ref> (1997) \n* ''Stephen's Test of Faith'' (1998) \n* ''St. Paul'' (a. k. a. Paul the Apostle)<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0270621/</ref> (2000)\n* ''St. Peter'' (2005-TV) \n* ''The Friends of Jesus - Thomas''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0276572/releaseinfo</ref> (2001) (Italy)\n* ''[[Apostle Peter and the Last Supper]]'' (2012) \n* ''[[A.D. The Bible Continues]]'' (2015 miniseries)\n* ''[[Paul, Apostle of Christ]]'' (2018)\n}}\n\n=== Creative ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''The Fourth Wise Man'' (1985)\n* ''[[Jesus of Montreal]] ''(French-Canadian) (1989)\n* ''[[Joshua (2002 film)|Joshua]]'' (2002)\n* ''[[Mary (2005 film)|Mary]]'' (2005)\n* ''Jesus Loves Me'' (2012) \n* ''He Knows My Name'' (2015)\n}}\n\n=== Revelation / Apocalypse ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|  * ''[[A Thief in the Night (film)|A Thief in the Night]]'' (1972) \n* ''[[The Omen]]'' (1976)\n* ''A Distant Thunder'' (1978)\n* ''[[The Late, Great Planet Earth]]'' (1979)\n* ''[[Image of the Beast (film)|Image of the Beast]]'' (1980) \n* ''Years of the Beast'' (1981)\n* ''Early Warning'' (1981) \n* ''[[The Prodigal Planet]]'' (1983) \n* ''[[The Seventh Sign]]'' (1988)\n* ''[[The Rapture (1991 film)|The Rapture]]'' (1991)\n* ''[[Apocalypse (film)|Apocalypse]]''