ilm)|The Sign of the Cross]]'' (1932) \n* ''[[Quo Vadis (1951 film)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (1951)\n* ''[[The Silver Chalice (film)|The Silver Chalice]]'' (1954)\n* ''[[Monty Python's Life of Brian]]'' (1979) (UK)\n* ''[[Quo Vadis? (1985 TV mini-series)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (1985 TV mini-series) (Italy)\n* ''[[Quo Vadis (2001 film)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (2001) (Poland)\n* ''[[Agora (film)|Agora]]'' (2009) (Spain)\n}}\n\n== Miracles and Apparitions ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[The Song of Bernadette (film)|The Song of Bernadette]]'' (1943)\n* ''[[The Miracle of Our Lady of Fatima]]'' (1952)\n* ''Miracle of Marcelino'' (1955)\n* ''[[The Reluctant Saint]]'' (1962)\n* ''[[Th\u00e9r\u00e8se (film)|Th\u00e9r\u00e8se]]'' (1986) (France) \n* ''Gospa'' (1995) (Croatia)\n* ''The Third Miracle'' (1999)\n* ''[[Stigmata (film)|Stigmata]]'' (1999) \n* ''Padre Pio'' (2000) (TV Movie) (Italy)  \n* ''Padre Pio: Tra cielo e terra'' (2000) (TV Movie) (Italy) \n}}\n\n==See also==\n* [[The Bible in film]]\n* [[Dramatic portrayals of Jesus Christ]]\n* [[Lists of movie source material]]\n* [[List of Islamic films]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Films Based On The Bible}}\n[[Category:Lists of films by source|Bible]]\n[[Category:Films based on the Bible| ]]\n[[Category:Bible-related lists]]\n[[Category:Lists of historical drama films]]\n\n[[it:The Chosen Prince, or The Friendship of David and Jonathan]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{Refimprove|date=January 2019}}\nThis is a list of movies (including television movies) based on the [[Bible]] ([[Old Testament]] and [[New Testament]]), depicting characters or figures from the Bible, or broadly derived from the revelations or interpretations therein.\n\n{{Inc-film}}\n== The Bible in general ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''Greatest Heroes of the Bible'' (TV series) (1978\u20131979)\n*''[[Superbook]]'' (animated TV series) (1981\u20131983; 2011\u2013present)\n*''[[Bible Collection]]'' (TV series) 