y)\n* ''[[Gideon: Tuba Warrior]]'' (2006)\n\n====Samson and Delilah - Judges 13-16====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Samson and Delilah (1922 film)|Samson and Delilah]]'' (1922)\n* ''[[Samson and Delilah (1949 film)|Samson and Delilah]]'' (1949)\n* ''[[Samson and Delilah (1984 film)|Samson and Delilah]]'' (1984)\n* ''[[Samson and Delilah (1996 film)|Samson and Delilah]]'' (1996, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[Samson (2018 film)|Samson]]'' (2018)\n}}\n\n====Ruth====\n* ''[[The Story of Ruth]]'' (1960)\n* ''[[The Book of Ruth: Journey of Faith]]'' (2009)\n\n===Kings of Israel===\n====David - First Samuel 16:1-First Kings 2:11====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''David et Goliath'' (France) (1910) \n* ''[[The Chosen Prince]]'' (1917)\n* ''[[David and Bathsheba (film)|David and Bathsheba]]'' (1951)\n* ''[[David and Goliath (1960 film)|David and Goliath]]'' (1960)\n* ''[[A Story of David]]'' (1961)\n* ''Saul and David'' (1964) \n* ''[[The Story of David]]'' (1976)\n* ''[[King David (film)|King David]]'' (1985)\n* ''[[Dave and the Giant Pickle]]'' (1996)\n* ''[[David (1997 film)|David]]'' (1997, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[King George and the Ducky]]'' (2000)\n* ''David and Goliath'' (2005, Liken Bible Series)\n* ''[[David and Goliath (film)|David and Goliath]]'' (2013)\n* ''David vs. Goliath'' (2016)\n* ''[[Of Kings and Prophets]]'' (2016, TV Miniseries)\n}}\n\n====Solomon - First Kings 1-11====\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[The Queen of Sheba (1921 film)|The Queen of Sheba]]'' (1921) \n* ''Haring Solomon at Reyna Sheba'' (1952) (Philippines)\n* ''[[La Regina di Saba]]'' (1952) (Italy)\n* ''[[Solomon and Sheba]]'' (1959)\n* ''[[Solomon & Sheba (1995 film)|Solomon & Sheba]]'' (1995) (TV) \n* ''[[Solomon (film)|Solomon]]'' (1997, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[The Kingdom of Solomon]]'' (2010) (Iran)\n}}\n\n===Prophets===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Sins of Jezebel]]'' (1953)\n* ''[[Jeremiah]]'' (1998, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[Jonah: A VeggieTales Movie]]'' (