 Visual Bible: Acts]]'' (1994) \n* ''The Emissary''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0219668/</ref> (1997) \n* ''Stephen's Test of Faith'' (1998) \n* ''St. Paul'' (a. k. a. Paul the Apostle)<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0270621/</ref> (2000)\n* ''St. Peter'' (2005-TV) \n* ''The Friends of Jesus - Thomas''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0276572/releaseinfo</ref> (2001) (Italy)\n* ''[[Apostle Peter and the Last Supper]]'' (2012) \n* ''[[A.D. The Bible Continues]]'' (2015 miniseries)\n* ''[[Paul, Apostle of Christ]]'' (2018)\n}}\n\n=== Creative ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''The Fourth Wise Man'' (1985)\n* ''[[Jesus of Montreal]] ''(French-Canadian) (1989)\n* ''[[Joshua (2002 film)|Joshua]]'' (2002)\n* ''[[Mary (2005 film)|Mary]]'' (2005)\n* ''Jesus Loves Me'' (2012) \n* ''He Knows My Name'' (2015)\n}}\n\n=== Revelation / Apocalypse ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|  * ''[[A Thief in the Night (film)|A Thief in the Night]]'' (1972) \n* ''[[The Omen]]'' (1976)\n* ''A Distant Thunder'' (1978)\n* ''[[The Late, Great Planet Earth]]'' (1979)\n* ''[[Image of the Beast (film)|Image of the Beast]]'' (1980) \n* ''Years of the Beast'' (1981)\n* ''Early Warning'' (1981) \n* ''[[The Prodigal Planet]]'' (1983) \n* ''[[The Seventh Sign]]'' (1988)\n* ''[[The Rapture (1991 film)|The Rapture]]'' (1991)\n* ''[[Apocalypse (film)|Apocalypse]]'' (1998)\n* ''[[Apocalypse II: Revelation]]'' (1999)\n* ''[[Apocalypse III: Tribulation]]'' (1999)\n* ''[[End of Days (film)|End of Days]]'' (1999)\n* ''[[The Moment After]]'' (1999) \n* ''[[The Omega Code]]'' (1999)\n* ''[[The Apocalypse (2000 film)|The Apocalypse]]'' (2000, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[Left Behind: The Movie]]'' (2000) (V) \n* ''[[Apocalypse IV: Judgment]]'' (2001)\n* ''[[Megiddo: The Omega Code 2]]'' (2001)\n* ''[[Left Behind II: Tribulation Force]]'' (2002) (V) \n* ''Apocalypse'' (2002, TNT Bible Series)\n* ''[[Six: The Mark Unleashed]]'' (2004) \n* ''[[Left Behind: World at War]]'' (2005) \n* ''The Poor Ones in the Paradise'' (2005)\n* ''[[The Moment After 2]]'' (2006) \n* ''[[Left Behind (2014 film)|Left Behind]]'' (2014)\n}}\n\n== Fictional interpolations ==\n\n===Adam and Eve===\n*''[[Mary's Incredible Dream]]'' (1976)\n* ''[[Year One]]'' (2009)\n* ''[[The Tragedy of Man]]'' (2011) (Hungary)\n\n===The Flood===\n* ''[[Evan Almighty]]'' (2007)\n\n===Moses===\n* ''[[Wholly Moses!]]'' (1980)\n* ''[[Seder-Masochism]]'' (2018)\n\n===Samson===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Hercules, Samson and Ulysses]]'' (1963)\n}}\n\n===David===\n* ''[[Kings (American TV series)|Kings]]'' (2009 TV series)\n\n===Esther===\n* ''Megillas Lester'' (2014)\n\n===Ben-Hur===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[Ben Hur (1907 film)|Ben Hur]]'' (1907 short) \n* ''[[Ben-Hur (1925 film)|Ben-Hur]]'' (1925) \n* ''[[Ben-Hur (1959 film)|Ben-Hur]]'' (1959) \n* ''[[Ben Hur (2003 film)|Ben Hur]]'' (2003) \n* ''[[Ben Hur (miniseries)|Ben Hur]]'' (2010) \n* ''[[Ben-Hur (2016 film)|Ben Hur]]'' (2016) \n}}\n\n===Early Christians===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[The Robe (film)|The Robe]]'' (1953)\n* ''[[Demetrius and the Gladiators]]'' (1954)\n* ''Quo Vadis?'' (1901) (France)\n* ''Quo Vadis?'' (1910) (France)\n* ''[[Quo Vadis (1913 film)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (1913) (Italy)\n* ''The Sign of the Cross'' (1914) \n* ''Quo Vadis?'' (1924) (Germany)\n* ''[[The Sign of the Cross (1932 film)|The Sign of the Cross]]'' (1932) \n* ''[[Quo Vadis (1951 film)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (1951)\n* ''[[The Silver Chalice (film)|The Silver Chalice]]'' (1954)\n* ''[[Monty Python's Life of Brian]]'' (1979) (UK)\n* ''[[Quo Vadis? (1985 TV mini-series)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (1985 TV mini-series) (Italy)\n* ''[[Quo Vadis (2001 film)|Quo Vadis?]]'' (2001) (Poland)\n* ''[[Agora (film)|Agora]]'' (2009) (Spain)\n}}\n\n== Miracles and Apparitions ==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=20em|\n* ''[[The Song of Bernadette (film)|The Song of Bernadette]]'' (1943)\n* ''[[The Miracle of Our Lady of Fatima]]'' (1952)\n* ''Miracle of Marcelino'' (1955)\n* ''[[The Reluctan